subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Julian Boyd scored 21 points and grabbed 20 rebounds, and Jamal Olasewere had 24 points as Long Island clinched the Northeast Conference regular-season title by defeating host Fairleigh Dickinson, 91-80.
